1. Get your manga link, for example: http://www.mangafox.com/manga/koe_de_oshigoto/
2. Extract series name from that link: koe_de_oshigoto
3. Paste it into field in application.
4. Change anything else, you want (thread number, page size)
5. Press "Check". Wait.
5.1. If application reports error, check, if you done everything correctly. Else press "Download".
6. Wait for manga download to complete.
7. You will find it in koe_de_oshigoto folder, that will appear in same place where application is.
